Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:31.42,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高举白旗的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:37.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在逃狱后的欢呼声中
