Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.80,0:22:47.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:52.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这定罪的把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:55.02,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇异的独角戏舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:57.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看着 竞争
