Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:13.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}许下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.25,0:23:15.88,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得赞美的惊恐
