Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:23.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引我吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:26.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}过于艳丽的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:28.43,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}带有偏见的分类
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:30.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信没有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:32.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你准备好了
